           <article class="art-post">
            <div class="art-postmetadataheader">
             <h2 class="art-postheader"><span class="art-postheadericon"><a href="/index.php/11-news/471-press-statement">Press Statement</a></span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="art-postcontent clearfix">
             <div class="art-article">
              <p>The Vice Chancellor Professor Eddie Mwenje would like to inform the valued stakeholders of the University that the Astra Campus was affected by flash floods on the 3rd January, 2015. Buildings, equipment and books were destroyed. As a result, teaching and learning activities will be affected for some time to come.</p> 
              <p>We would like to assure our stakeholders that every effort is being made to restore the campus to normalcy.</p> 
              <p>We appreciate your support and cooperation during this difficult period.</p> 
              <p>Registrar</p>
             </div>
             <div class="kmt-readon"> 
              <span class="kmt-comment aligned-right"> <a href="http://www.buse.ac.zw/index.php/11-news/471-press-statement#section-kmt">Comment (0)</a> </span> 
              <span class="kmt-hits aligned-right"> Hits: 33 </span> 
             </div>
            </div>
           </article>
