             <h2 class="art-postheader"><span class="art-postheadericon"><a href="/index.php/11-news/469-special-examinations-november-december-2014-examinations">Special Examinations (November/December 2014 Examinations)</a></span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="art-postcontent clearfix">
             <div class="art-article">
              <ul> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">All results for November/December 2014 examinations are out. &nbsp;Students are advised to clear outstanding fees to access their results through the e-learning portal.</span></li> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">Special Examinations will be conducted from Monday 9 March to Friday 13 March 2015 at the Main Campus.</span></li> 
              </ul> 
              <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; For enquiries contact the Examinations Office on 0772154880-6 Extension 1013 or the respective departments.</p> 
              <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="/downloads/list.pdf">Click here to download the list for candidates offered Special Examinations</a></p> 
