             <h2 class="art-postheader"><span class="art-postheadericon"><a href="/index.php/11-news/450-registration-notice-for-returning-students-march-2015">Registration Notice For Returning Students March 2015</a></span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="art-postcontent clearfix">
             <div class="art-article">
              <ul> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">All returning students are informed that they will be expected to register on line first then manually at their respective departments.</span></li> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">Students are expected to pay the requisite fees first (i.e. at least $300.00 for undergraduate degree programmes and $200.00 for diploma programmes).Please be informed that all outstanding fees balances should be paid by the end of the semester break(10 April 2015)</span></li> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">Students should log on to their e-learning platform and follow the prescribed procedure carefully.</span></li> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">Those who face any challenges should follow the communication procedure prescribed or as a last resort contact ICT on (0271)7531/2/3/5/6, 7621-4, 0772 154 880/2/5/7/8 extension 1035 or registration office on extension 1032.</span></li> 
              </ul> 
              <p><strong>Registration dates &nbsp;</strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p> 
              <ul> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">Normal registration &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 16-27 February 2015</span></li> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">Late registration &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;: 2-13 March 2015</span></li> 
               <li><span style="color: #2f2b23;">End of registration (all students) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; : 13 March 2015.</span></li> 
              </ul>
             </div>
