             <h2 class="art-postheader"><span class="art-postheadericon"><a href="/index.php/11-news/446-march-august-2015-admissions">March/August 2015 Admissions</a></span></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="art-postcontent clearfix">
             <div class="art-article">
              <p>The University invites suitably qualified applicants to be enrolled in the programmes on offer as detailed below:&nbsp;</p> 
              <p style="text-align: justify;">All candidates who apply for degree programmes should have the specified ‘A’ Level subjects and at least 5 ‘O’ Level subjects including English Language and Mathematics. Candidates applying for Diplomas and Certificates must have the relevant 5 ‘O’ Level subjects including Mathematics and English Language. The Mathematics Bridging Course will only be offered for programmes as indicated.</p> 
             </div>
             <div class="kmt-readon"> 
              <span class="kmt-readmore aligned-right"> <a href="http://www.buse.ac.zw/index.php/11-news/446-march-august-2015-admissions" title="March/August 2015 Admissions">Read More</a> </span> 
